<main>
  <section id="product" >
    <div>
      <h1>Cool project collaboration for your teams !</h1>
      <p>Say hello to a user-friendly collaboration app that save your team work time.</p>
      <%= link_to 'Get started', signup_path, data: { turbo: false }, class: "btn-contact" %>
    </div>
    <section>
      <%= image_tag "header magnet-me-63XrEEiOko8-unsplash.jpg", alt: "Collaborator on project" %>
      <%= image_tag "header windows-N1YOSWrXQJE-unsplash.jpg", alt: "Collaborator on project" %>
      <span>Stay organized</span>
      <span>Manage your project</span>
      <span>Assign task issues</span>
    </section>
  </section>

  <section id="feature">
    <h2>Features</h2>
    <div>
      <article>
        <div>
          <h3>Assign task issues</h3>
          <p>Organize and assign task issues for collaborators so they can see immediately what they need to do, and when work is due.</p>
        </div>
        <%= image_tag "feature-issues.png", alt: "Feature issues screenshot" %>
      </article>
      <article>
        <div>
          <h3>Chat with others collaborators</h3>
          <p>Communicate easily on project, and keep everyone up to date</p>
        </div>
        <%= image_tag "feature-chat.png", alt: "Feature chat screenshot" %>
      </article>
      <article>
        <div>
          <h3>Store all files in documents</h3>
          <p>Store projects documents efficiently in one place in just one click.</p>
        </div>
        <%= image_tag "feature-documents.png", alt: "Feature documents screenshot" %>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="testimonial">
    <h2>Clients and teams of all sizes love our app.</h2>
    <div>
      <article>
        <%= image_tag "testimonial abbas-malek-hosseini-JC1oue4zY5U-unsplash.jpg", alt: "Client testimonial" %>
        <p>Employees collaborations are so easy with Coolab.</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <%= image_tag "testimonial christina-wocintechchat-com-0Zx1bDv5BNY-unsplash.jpg", alt: "Client testimonial" %>
        <p>It has never been easier to manage our project.</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <%= image_tag "testimonial christina-wocintechchat-com-SJvDxw0azqw-unsplash.jpg", alt: "Client testimonial" %>
        <p>Having all of our projects in one app is really cool!</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <%= image_tag "testimonial batel-studio-ttSRjiYG_WM-unsplash.jpg", alt: "Client testimonial" %>
        <p>It helps me to prioritize tasks and improve work productivity.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="pricing">
    <h2>Pricing </h2>
    <p>Adapt for all sizes, get started for free.</p>
    <div>
      <article class="card">
        <h3 class="fs-large">Free</h3>
        <p><span>$0</span>/month</p>
        <%= link_to 'Get started', signup_path, data: { turbo: false }, class: "btn-outline-primary" %>
        <p>Basic includes:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>
